Replaces: libnautilus-extension1a, libnautilus-extension1
Breaks: nautilus (<< 1:3.0)
Description: libraries for eos-file-manager components - runtime version
 eos-file-manager is the official file manager for the EOS desktop.
 .
 This package contains a few runtime libraries needed by eos-file-manager's extensions.

